### Public page
GET http://localhost:8080/

### Post comment
POST http://localhost:8080/comment/create
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

Comment[name]=Smoke&Comment[message]=Hello from smoke test

### Admin login
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

LoginForm[username]=admin&LoginForm[password]=admin123

### Admin comments
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/comments

### Reject empty comment message
# Expected: 200 OK with "Message cannot be blank."
POST http://localhost:8080/comment/create
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

Comment[name]=Smoke&Comment[message]=

### Reject invalid admin login
# Expected: 200 OK with "Incorrect login or password."
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

LoginForm[username]=admin&LoginForm[password]=wrong-password

### Redirect guest away from admin comments
# Expected: 302 Found with Location: /admin/login
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/comments
